但是在做自关联的时候，吞吐会低很多，所以结果还是会比较久。同样的join SQL在CK上执行3s以内可以出结果，doris需要44s
代码如下
``` SQL
select
    a.app_name, a.user_id, b.province
from
    (
        -- group by后400w数据
        select 
            app_name
            ,user_id 
        from 
            test_duplicate_table
        where 
            server_timestamp between '2022-11-02 00:00:00' and '2022-11-03 00:00:00'
        group by 
            app_name
            ,user_id
    ) a
left join
    (
        select 
            app_name
            ,user_id
            ,max(province) as province
        from 
            test_duplicate_table
        where 
            server_timestamp between '2022-11-02 00:00:00' and '2022-11-03 00:00:00'
        group by 
            app_name
            ,user_id
    ) b on b.user_id = a.user_id and b.app_name = a.app_name
limit 10
```
